commit.message:
(CPP_SPEC): Define __PTRDIFF_TYPE__ and __mips.

(PTRDIFF_TYPE): Delete.
(SIZE_TYPE): Define.
(SET_ASM_OP): Define.

From-SVN: r7203

 %{.m:	-D__LANGUAGE_OBJECTIVE_C__ -D__LANGUAGE_OBJECTIVE_C} \
-%{!.S:%{!.s:	-D__LANGUAGE_C__  -D__LANGUAGE_C %{!ansi:-DLANGUAGE_C}}}"
